2340  [DllImport(NativeLibName, EntryPoint = "SDL_ShowMessageBox", CallingConvention = CallingConvention.Cdecl)]

2343 
2349  [return: NotNull]
2350  private static IntPtr INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(string str)
2351  {
2352  if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(str))
2353  {
2354  return IntPtr.Zero;
2355  }
2356 
2357  byte[] bytes = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str + '\0');
2358  IntPtr mem = INTERNAL_SDL_malloc(bytes.Length);
2359  Marshal.Copy(bytes, 0, mem, bytes.Length);
2360  return mem;
2361  }
2362 
2369  public static int ShowMessageBox(ref SdlMessageBoxData messageBoxData, out int buttonId)
2370  {
2371  InternalSdlMessageBoxData data = new InternalSdlMessageBoxData
2372  {
2373  flags = messageBoxData.flags,
2374  window = messageBoxData.window,
2375  title = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageBoxData.title),
2376  message = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageBoxData.message),
2377  numbuttons = messageBoxData.numbuttons
2378  };
2379 
2380  InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData[] buttons = new InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData[messageBoxData.numbuttons];
2381  IntPtr buttonsPtr = IntPtr.Zero;
2382 
2383  try
2384  {
2385  for (int i = 0; i < messageBoxData.numbuttons; i++)
2386  {
2387  buttons[i] = new InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData
2388  {
2389  flags = messageBoxData.buttons[i].flags,
2390  buttonId = messageBoxData.buttons[i].buttonId,
2391  text = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageBoxData.buttons[i].text)
2392  };
2393  }
2394 
2395  buttonsPtr = Marshal.AllocHGlobal(buttons.Length * Marshal.SizeOf<InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData>());
2396  for (int i = 0; i < buttons.Length; i++)
2397  {
2398  IntPtr buttonPtr = buttonsPtr + i * Marshal.SizeOf<InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData>();
2399  Marshal.StructureToPtr(buttons[i], buttonPtr, false);
2400  }
2401 
2402  data.buttons = buttonsPtr;
2403 
2404  IntPtr colorSchemePtr = IntPtr.Zero;
2405  if (messageBoxData.colorScheme != null)
2406  {
2407  colorSchemePtr = Marshal.AllocHGlobal(Marshal.SizeOf<SdlMessageBoxColorScheme>());
2408  Marshal.StructureToPtr(messageBoxData.colorScheme.Value, colorSchemePtr, false);
2409  }
2410 
2411  int result = INTERNAL_SDL_ShowMessageBox(ref data, out buttonId);
2412 
2413  for (int i = 0; i < messageBoxData.numbuttons; i++)
2414  {
2415  INTERNAL_SDL_free(buttons[i].text);
2416  }
2417 
2418  INTERNAL_SDL_free(data.message);
2419  INTERNAL_SDL_free(data.title);
2420 
2421  if (colorSchemePtr != IntPtr.Zero)
2422  {
2423  Marshal.DestroyStructure<SdlMessageBoxColorScheme>(colorSchemePtr);
2424  Marshal.FreeHGlobal(colorSchemePtr);
2425  }
2426 
2427  return result;
2428  }
2429  finally
2430  {
2431  if (buttonsPtr != IntPtr.Zero)
2432  {
2433  Marshal.FreeHGlobal(buttonsPtr);
2434  }
2435  }
2436  }

4839  [return: NotNull]
4840  private static uint SdlDefinePixelFormat(PixelType type, uint order, PackedLayout layout, byte bits, byte bytes) => (uint) ((1 << 28) | ((byte) type << 24) | ((byte) order << 20) | ((byte) layout << 16) | (bits << 8) | bytes);

4881 
4887  [return: NotNull]
4888  public static byte SdlBytesPerPixel(uint x)
4889  {
4890  if (SdlIsPixelFormatFour(x))
4891  {
4892  if (x == PixelFormatYuy2 ||
4893  x == PixelFormatUy ||
4894  x == PixelFormatYv)
4895  {
4896  return 2;
4897  }
4898 
4899  return 1;
4900  }
4901 
4902  return (byte) (x & 0xFF);
4903  }

4910  [return: NotNull]
4911  public static bool SdlIsPixelFormatIndexed(uint format)
4912  {
4913  if (SdlIsPixelFormatFour(format))
4914  {
4915  return false;
4916  }
4917 
4918  PixelType pType =
4919  (PixelType) SdlPixelType(format);
4920  return pType == PixelType.PixelTypeIndex1 ||
4921  pType == PixelType.PixelTypeIndex4 ||
4922  pType == PixelType.PixelTypeIndex8;
4923  }
4924 
4930  [return: NotNull]
4931  private static bool SdlIsPixelFormatPacked(uint format)
4932  {
4933  if (SdlIsPixelFormatFour(format))
4934  {
4935  return false;
4936  }
4937 
4938  PixelType pType =
4939  (PixelType) SdlPixelType(format);
4940  return pType == PixelType.PixelTypePacked8 ||
4941  pType == PixelType.PixelTypePacked16 ||
4942  pType == PixelType.PixelTypePacked32;
4943  }
4944 
4950  [return: NotNull]
4951  private static bool SdlIsPixelFormatArray(uint format)
4952  {
4953  if (SdlIsPixelFormatFour(format))
4954  {
4955  return false;
4956  }
4957 
4958  PixelType pType =
4959  (PixelType) SdlPixelType(format);
4960  return pType == PixelType.PixelTypeArrayU8 ||
4961  pType == PixelType.PixelTypeArrayU16 ||
4962  pType == PixelType.PixelTypeArrayU32 ||
4963  pType == PixelType.PixelTypeArrayF16 ||
4964  pType == PixelType.PixelTypeArrayF32;
4965  }
4966 
4972  [return: NotNull]
4973  public static bool SdlIsPixelFormatAlpha(uint format)
4974  {
4975  if (SdlIsPixelFormatPacked(format))
4976  {
4977  PackedOrder pOrder =
4978  (PackedOrder) SdlPixelOrder(format);
4979  return pOrder == PackedOrder.PackedOrderARgb ||
4980  pOrder == PackedOrder.PackedOrderRGba ||
4981  pOrder == PackedOrder.PackedOrderABgr ||
4982  pOrder == PackedOrder.PackedOrderBGra;
4983  }
4984 
4985  if (SdlIsPixelFormatArray(format))
4986  {
4987  SdlArrayOrder aOrder =
4988  (SdlArrayOrder) SdlPixelOrder(format);
4989  return aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderArgb ||
4990  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderRgba ||
4991  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderAbgr ||
4992  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderBgra;
4993  }
4994 
4995  return false;
4996  }

8100  public static ushort SdlAudioBitSize(ushort x) => (ushort) (x & AudioMaskBitSize);

8107  public static bool SdlAudioIsFloat(ushort x) => (x & AudioMaskDatatype) != 0;
8108 
8114  public static bool SdlAudioIsBigEndian(ushort x) => (x & AudioMaskEndian) != 0;
8115 
8121  public static bool SdlAudioIsSigned(ushort x) => (x & AudioMaskSigned) != 0;
8122 
8128  public static bool SdlAudioIsInt(ushort x) => (x & AudioMaskDatatype) == 0;
8129 
8135  public static bool SdlAudioIsLittleEndian(ushort x) => (x & AudioMaskEndian) == 0;
8136 
8142  public static bool SdlAudioIsUnsigned(ushort x) => (x & AudioMaskSigned) == 0;
